td test keys — TEST FIXTURES ONLY. Committed fixtures so builds stay
reproducible (a key generated at build time would not be). Do not reuse
the keypair for anything.

td_m12_signify{.sec,.pub} is a throwaway signify (ed25519) keypair used solely
by the M12 signed-distribution rungs (system/td-registry.scm and the placer's
verify-then-place tests): the registry derivation signs each pushed image's
manifest-digest statement with the .sec key, and the rungs verify with the
.pub key. It signs nothing but loop-internal test artifacts and is trusted by
nothing outside the loop's own assertions.
